  \medskip
  \begin{tabular}{cl}
    Intelligence & Timeframe \\
    3–8 & monthly \\
    9–12 & weekly \\
    13–18 & daily \\
  \end{tabular}}

\emph{Water breathing} (3\rd circle) allows one target to breathe
underwater for one day.

\textbf{Numbers}: 2d20. A underwater lair of nixies and their charmed
victims are usually protected by as many \hyperref[sec:fish]{giant
  fish} as there are nixies.

\textbf{Names}: Dahlia, Lily, Poppy, Hawthorn, Hyacinth, Lotus.

\poor The poor men lured into their underwater domains might have left
a little treasure.

